column1: Would the lifting of the federal government’s social distancing guidelines change how you go about your life?

column2: Yes, I would go out and meet people the way I did before the virus outbreak
column3: Yes, I would go out and meet people more, but I would be cautious about it
column4: No, I would stick to staying home and keeping away from people
column5: No, I was never staying home or keeping away from people anyway
